{"about_the_game":"This is a game all about relaxing and hitting some cool drifts. Try the different modes and drift your way to the top of leaderboard, if you can...                                  <br>Drift or drive to earn cash and save up for one of the 15 cars to choose from\u2014one of them being a little more unique than usual. Also, there are several built-in playlists that you can select and drift to in any mode! Please note this game is still a work in progress and I do update constantly. As a solo dev I love any and all feedback in attempts to improve and truly make this a better game for everyone &lt; 3<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Special Controls ( Not essential but a whole lotta fun )</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Super Jump: Hold 'L SHIFT' to activate slo-motion then hold 'SPACE' or 'F' to super jump ;)<br></li><li> Flip Mid-Air: While high up in the air. Hold S to bring speed below 50 then hold 'E' to start flipping</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Custom Playlists</h2>In addition, there is a custom playlist feature that allows you to drift to any playlist you want while watching the visual waveforms of the song move around you!<br>This feature works with .Wav and .Mp3 from what I have tested.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Solid Drifter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2613610/833559db9e3c92822d8e98eae5a58015c2e8144f.jpg"},{"name":"Advanced Drifter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2613610/f28d8a7e7cf1161f326db1f4ff04aadd1d4f44ee.jpg"},{"name":"Pro Drifter","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2613610/79df66d1d61f51f9d2672efe270e36232a7400e5.jpg"},{"name":"Shopper","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2613610/c3a6dc7cfb4d581a58577d07ff9e93016f25dbbe.jpg"},{"name":"Big Spender","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2613610/11a1600ed08904e9ab9b4f3e